"2025-11-19T00:33:57-08:00", "__typename": "Post"}}, {"id": "1130314", "slug": "readmeeting-2", "name": "ReadMeeting", "tagline": "AI-powered meeting summaries with team collaboration.", "logoUuid": "0f0019a9-25d3-498b-a895-cd69909d47a5.jpeg", "reviewsRating": 0.0, "reviewsCount": 0, "categories": [{"id": "40", "name": "Video conferencing", "slug": "video-conferencing", "path": "/categories/video-conferencing", "__typename": "ProductCategory"}, {"id": "1288", "name": "AI notetakers", "slug": "ai-meeting-notetakers", "path": "/categories/ai-meeting-notetakers", "__typename": "ProductCategory"}, {"id": "1804", "name": "Transcription", "slug": "transcription", "path": "/categories/transcription", "__typename": "ProductCategory"}], "tags": ["meeting recording", "ai-generated summaries", "automatic transcription", "pdf export", "action item extraction", "productivity", "meetings", "artificial intelligence", "video conferencing", "ai meeting notetakers", "transcription"], "embeddingSummary": null, "isTopProduct": false, "badges": {"edges": [], "__typename": "Connection"}, "followersCount": 83, "isSubscribed": false, "__typename": "Product", "isNoLongerOnline": false, "latestLaunch": {"id": "1041810", "scheduledAt": "2025-11-25T00:01:00-08:00", "__typename": "Post"}}], "__typename": "ProductsSummary"}, "recentLaunches": {"totalCount": 109, "__typename": "ProductsConnection"}, "questions": [], "discussions": {"edges": [{"node": {"id": "700264", "pageViewsCount": 1767, "slug": "with-so-many-new-ai-note-takers-what-s-your-favorite-and-why", "createdAt": "2025-05-16T06:24:21-07:00", "path": "/p/granola/with-so-many-new-ai-note-takers-what-s-your-favorite-and-why", "title": "With so many new AI Note Takers - what's your favorite and why?", "descriptionPreview": "<p>I've tested so many AI Note takers as of late. @Fathom, @Fireflies.ai , BuildBetter, @Grain, and even Google's Transcribing feature. They're all pretty good but lately @Granola has been winning me over.</p><p>BuildBetter is really good for teams, has a nice chat function that lets you chat across all your meetings and get good insight from your team members, calls, clients, etc. <br>But for personal, and individual notes - Granola is a champion. Recently I've been using Granola's new mobile app for in-person convos and it's amazing. Particularly for my conversations in Japanese, where the chances of me misinterpreting something, missing a key note, or simply not knowing a word are higher. Granola captures all key points and topics and WRITES THE NOTES IN ENGLISH. <br>Literal immediate translating assistant. I'm not sure if other's do this, but Granola has been the easiest to quickly boot up and get my notes in a snap...without needing to translate.<br>I'm curious what everyone else uses and why!</p>", "featuredAt": null, "pinned": false, "user": {"id": "84553", "name": "Gabe Perez", "username": "gabe", "avatarUrl": "https://ph-avatars.imgix.net/84553/afd8c28f-5881-4a33-aa3d-9bc02e32c192.jpeg", "__typename": "User", "isAccountVerified": true, "isAmbassador": false, "selectedBylineProduct": {"id": "112572", "name": "Product Hunt", "slug": "producthunt", "logoUuid": "d618ea86-70ae-4d12-8ec2-0ed78c723ddf.png", "isNoLongerOnline": false, "__typename": "Product"}, "topProductBadge": null, "topHunterBadge": null, "topLaunchBadge": null}, "hasVoted": false, "votesCount": 36, "__typename": "DiscussionThread", "commentsCount": 26, "featuredComment": null, "primaryForum": {"id": "134552", "slug": "granola", "subject": {"id": "584337", "name": "Granola", "logoUuid": "c471aadb-c3d9-4676-8fe8-0089ad45779a.png", "__typename": "Product"}, "__typename": "DiscussionForumType"}}, "__typename": "DiscussionThreadEdge"}, {"node": {"id": "200606", "pageViewsCount": 218, "slug": "do-you-use-ai-powered-software-to-record-meeting-notes-if-so-what-do-you-use", "createdAt": "2023-03-27T07:00:42-07:00", "path": "/p/general/do-you-use-ai-powered-software-to-record-meeting-notes-if-so-what-do-you-use", "title": "Do you use AI-powered software to record meeting notes? If so, what do you use?", "descriptionPreview": "I've tried using tools that automatically take notes during my Zoom/Google Meet calls, but none of them have stuck. A full transcription is overkill and summaries often miss the most important points. Additional context: Most of my calls are fundraising-related conversations with founders. I would prefer NOT to have a \"bot\" join a call and ideally the notes could automatically be shared in a specific Slack channel with my team. I'm curious what tools people are using and for what use cases. I'd appreciate any recommendations. :)", "featuredAt": "2023-03-28", "pinned": false, "user": {"id": "2", "name": "Ryan Hoover", "username": "rrhoover", "avatarUrl": "https://ph-avatars.imgix.net/2/original.jpeg", "__typename": "User", "isAccountVerified": true, "isAmbassador": false, "selectedBylineProduct": {"id": "112572", "name": "Product Hunt", "slug": "producthunt", "logoUuid": "d618ea86-70ae-4d12-8ec2-0ed78c723ddf.png", "isNoLongerOnline": false, "__typename": "Product"}, "topProductBadge": null, "topHunterBadge": null, "topLaunchBadge": null}, "hasVoted": false, "votesCount": 136, "__typename": "DiscussionThread", "commentsCount": 121, "featuredComment": null, "primaryForum": {"id": "7", "slug": "general", "subject": {"id": "100", "name": "General", "thumbnailUuid": "85c8f053-f68f-486f-a83b-79bd21080edc.svg", "__typename": "DiscussionCategory"}, "__typename": "DiscussionForumType"}}, "__typename": "DiscussionThreadEdge"}, {"node": {"id": "692604", "pageViewsCount": 470, "slug": "ai-tools-i-m-using-now", "createdAt": "2025-04-28T10:02:58-07:00", "path": "/p/general/ai-tools-i-m-using-now", "title": "AI tools I'm using now", "descriptionPreview": "<p>I was recently talking with a group of founders, and we went around sharing tools we're using now. Posting my notes for our community here - would love to know what else people are using!</p><p>Voice AI toolkit:</p><p>- Vapi</p>", "featuredAt": null, "pinned": false, "user": {"id": "466162", "name": "Rajiv Ayyangar", "username": "rajiv_ayyangar", "avatarUrl": "https://ph-avatars.imgix.net/466162/27f2ba7f-a0e1-4253-bb12-86581d91c20b.jpeg", "__typename": "User", "isAccountVerified": true, "isAmbassador": false, "selectedBylineProduct": {"id": "112572", "name": "Product Hunt", "slug": "producthunt", "logoUuid": "d618ea86-70ae-4d12-8ec2-0ed78c723ddf.png", "isNoLongerOnline": false, "__typename": "Product"}, "topProductBadge": null, "topHunterBadge": null, "topLaunchBadge": null}, "hasVoted": false, "votesCount": 46, "__typename": "DiscussionThread", "commentsCount": 10, "featuredComment": null, "primaryForum": {"id": "7", "slug": "general", "subject": {"id": "100", "name": "General", "thumbnailUuid": "85c8f053-f68f-486f-a83b-79bd21080edc.svg", "__typename": "DiscussionCategory"}, "__typename": "DiscussionForumType"}}, "__typename": "DiscussionThreadEdge"}, {"node": {"id": "678649", "pageViewsCount": 630, "slug": "what-is-the-best-ai-notetaking-tool-that-doesn-t-actually-join-the-call", "createdAt": "2025-03-05T08:58:48-08:00", "path": "/p/general/what-is-the-best-ai-notetaking-tool-that-doesn-t-actually-join-the-call", "title": "What is the best AI notetaking tool that doesn\u2019t actually \u201cjoin\u201d the call? ", "descriptionPreview": "<p>I ve been curious to try an AI notetaking tool that doesn t loudly announce itself when joining a call and only shares the notes afterwards with me.</p><p>I guess this is starting to become more commonplace but it still feels (to me) like an intruder in the call, and like I should ask permission (just as when someone records the call - I m honestly not sure there is really any difference).</p>", "featuredAt": null, "pinned": false, "user": {"id": "3774512", "name": "Leeann Trang", "username": "leeanntrang", "avatarUrl": "https://ph-avatars.imgix.net/3774512/original.png", "__typename": "User", "isAccountVerified": true, "isAmbassador": false